{"query":" mutation createPerson(
    $relationship: Relationship
    $providerId: ID
    $referentId: ID
    $emailPerso: String
    $firstName: String!
    $secondName: String
    $thirdName: String!
    $lastName: String
    $birthdate: Date
    $mainMobile: String
    $secondaryMobile: String
    $mainAddress: String
    $secondaryAddress: String
    $poBox: String
    $city: String
    $isBeneficiary: Boolean
  ) {
    createPerson(
      input: {
        emailPerso: $emailPerso
        thirdName: $thirdName
        mainMobile: $mainMobile
        city: $city
        birthdate: $birthdate
        secondName: $secondName
        mainAddress: $mainAddress
        lastName: $lastName
        firstName: $firstName
        relationship: $relationship
        isBeneficiary: $isBeneficiary
        poBox: $poBox
        secondaryMobile: $secondaryMobile
        referentId: $referentId
        providerId: $providerId
        secondaryAddress: $secondaryAddress
      }
    ) {
      person {
        id
        emailPro
        firstName
        sexe
        thirdName
      }
      message
    }
  }","operationName":"createPerson"}

			person{

  }","variables":{"id":"UGVyc29uTm9kZTplMzY1OGNhMi05MjczLTQwMWEtYWFmMC02ZjVlMDA1ZGQ4MDY=","emailPro":"darlynnpro@gmail.com","city":"Douala","poBox":"2370","mainAddress":"BP Cite"},"operationName":"updatePerson"}

{"query":"mutation createCompany(
    $category: ProviderCategory
    $name: String!
    $website: String
    $email: String
    $city: String
    $secondaryAddress: String
    $activitySectorIdList: [ID]
    $specialityIdList: [ID]
    $prestationIdList: [ID]
    $isHealthCare: Boolean
    $headCompanySlug: String
  ) {
    createCompany(
      input: {
        category: $category
        name: $name
        website: $website
        email: $email
        city: $city
        secondaryAddress: $secondaryAddress
        activitySectorIdList: $activitySectorIdList
        specialityIdList: $specialityIdList
        prestationIdList: $prestationIdList
        isHealthCare: $isHealthCare
        headCompanySlug: $headCompanySlug
      }
    ) {
      message
    }
  }
","variables":{"name":"BICEC Yaounde","headCompanySlug":"bicec"},"operationName":"createCompany"}

{"query":"mutation updateMutualist(
	$role: Role
	$situation: Situation
	$id: ID!
	$email: String
	$mobile: String
	$categoryId: ID
	$permissionGroupId: ID
	$hiringDate: Date
	$agencyId: ID
	$closingDate: Date
	$isStaff: Boolean
	$revokePermissionGroup: Boolean
	$revokeCategory: Boolean
) {
	updateMutualist(
		input: {
			role: $role
			id: $id
			email: $email
			situation: $situation
			mobile: $mobile
			categoryId: $categoryId
			permissionGroupId: $permissionGroupId
			hiringDate: $hiringDate
			closingDate: $closingDate
			agencyId: $agencyId
			isStaff: $isStaff
			revokePermissionGroup: $revokePermissionGroup
			revokeCategory: $revokeCategory
		}
	) {
		mutualist {
			id
			email
			mobile
			role
      isStaff
			situation
		}
		message
	}
}
","variables":{"id":"TWVtYmVyTm9kZTo0NjAwZWIzNi1kMzA4LTQzNWMtOTU2Zi04ZjVjMmEzNDRmNzM=","situation":"INACTIVE"},"operationName":"updateMutualist"}

{"query":" query mutualists(
    $first: Int
    $offset: Int
    $category: ID
    $email: String
    $categoryPkNotEqual: String
    $categoryPk: String
    $personFirstName: String
    $personSecondName: String
    $personThirdName: String
    $personLastName: String
    $personCity: String
    $matricule: String
    $situation: String
    $isArchived: String
		$situation_Icontains: String
  ) {
    mutualists(
      first: $first
      offset: $offset
      category: $category
      email: $email
      categoryPkNotEqual: $categoryPkNotEqual
      categoryPk: $categoryPk
      personFirstName: $personFirstName
      personSecondName: $personSecondName
      personThirdName: $personThirdName
      personLastName: $personLastName
      personCity: $personCity
      matricule: $matricule
      situation: $situation
      isArchived: $isArchived
			situation_Icontains: $situation_Icontains
    ) {
      pageInfo {
        endCursor
        hasNextPage
        hasPreviousPage
        startCursor
      }
      totalCount
      edges {
        node {
          id
          email
          mobile
          matricule
          hiringDate
          closingDate
          situation
          isArchived
          agency {
            id
            name
          }
          bankaccount {
            id
            number
            iban
            swift
            openOn
            status
            type
            balance
            forecastBalance
            ownerLabel
            moralOwner {
              category
            }
          }
          category {
            id
            name
            title
          }
          person {
            id
            firstName
            thirdName
            lastName
            secondName
            mainMobile
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }","variables":{"situation_Icontains":"RETRAITE"},"operationName":"mutualists"}
